Class Change

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jlibsedml.SEDBase
      • org.jlibsedml.Change
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AddXML, ChangeAttribute, ChangeXML, ComputeChange, RemoveXML

    public abstract class Change
extends SEDBase
    Abstract class for ChangeXXX classes that manipulate a Model. This class is not intended to be sub-classed by clients.
    Author:
    anu/radams

        public abstract String getChangeKind()
        Type definition of the type of change to be applied.
        Returns one of:
        • SEDMLTags.CHANGE_ATTRIBUTE_KIND
        • SEDMLTags.CHANGE_XML_KIND
        • SEDMLTags.ADD_XML_KIND
        • SEDMLTags.REMOVE_XML_KIND
        • SEDMLTags.COMPUTE_CHANGE_KIND
        • SET_VALUE_KIND
        Returns:
        a String for the type of change element.
